attributes.background:
In support of the NUT strike, we want an increase in funding for schools (in the face of imminent cuts and likely redundancies);

Guaranteed terms and conditions across all types of schools;

National negotiations to reduce chronic workload problems.

attributes.additional_details:
For the Royal Navy and the Army, any previous amount of service is acceptable. The RAF requires that previous service falls into one of the following categories: 

•	had war time RAF service exceeding 6 months between 3 Sep 1939 and 8 Aug 1945. Or;
•	completed 16yrs officer service. Or;
•	completed 20yrs airman service. Or;
•	completed a combination of officer and airman service exceeding 16yrs.
